name: Six Spheres - #6 of 6
description:
006.6 - A dazzling, vivid, and chaotic sphere, floating wildly in space. Entering this space is only for those who dare to have their senses thrown about until all objects fades to a blurred sea of atoms and you emerge reborn with the eyes of a child. Some forces are best admired from a distance. 

🔊 Audio by Oniero
